verse 2: She said, "It grieves me now to see you in such pain I wish there was somethin' I could do to make smile again." I said, " I appreciate that, and could you please explain About the fifty ways?" She said, "Why don't we both just sleep on it tonight I'm Sure in the morning you'll begin to see the light." And then she kissed me and I realized she probably was right There muyst be fifty ways to leave your lover Fifty ways to leave your lover.
Just slip out the back Jack....
